freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I am on day 7 of quadruple therapy for h. Pylori.  Having rash associated with doxycycline,  nausea and upset GI tract due to the other meds, dizziness due to flagyl. I doubt that any of these sx are from my Pfizer COVID vaccine

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I felt flushed a few times,  not as much as yesterday.  Headache is mostly gone.
I think the nausea is related to my GERD.
Sweating and felt flushed intermittently,  no actual fever
Sweating with feeling flushed several times. I took zofran for the nausea.
